Package: Advanced_ggplot
Title: A Modern Object-Oriented Data Visualization Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Christopher", "Odoom", email = "odoomchristopher22@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modern and flexible data visualization package for R, designed 
    to provide an alternative to ggplot2 with a clean, composable API and fully 
    object-oriented design using R6 classes. The package supports a variety of 
    geometries including points, lines, bars, histograms, density plots, boxplots, 
    and more, along with advanced features like faceting, custom themes, 
    annotations, and animations.
